tunnel forwarding, mining pool connection management, fee scheduling,
statistics, web administration, and operational management;

3.3 deploy and configure the Software within infrastructure owned or lawfully
managed by the User;

3.4 distribute, mirror, or re-host Unmodified Release Packages to third
parties, provided that all of the following conditions are met:

(a) no Software Fee is charged;

(b) the distribution source is clearly identified as official or non-official,
and no non-official mirror is implied to be an Official Release;

