provided so third parties can obtain official verification information;

(d) this Agreement in full, copyright notices, trademark notices, and all
proprietary markings included in the Official Release are included;

(e) checksums, security notices, network-exposure warnings, and disclaimers
included in the Official Release are not removed, modified, hidden, or
weakened.

3.5 This Agreement grants no trademark rights, Source Code rights, patent
rights, or other rights except those expressly stated in this Article.

Article 4. Restrictions

The User shall not:

